data.description: Welcome to your new home at 1131 Nelson Meadow Ln, Poinciana, FL! This exquisite property offers 4 bedrooms, with a flexible room converted into a bonus room, along with 2.5 baths. Discover a spacious master bedroom featuring a tile shower and tile flooring for added luxury. This two-story home conveniently places all rooms, including the laundry room, on the second floor. The ground floor features an open floor plan, with the kitchen showcasing granite countertops and a sliding door leading to the backyard. Enjoy the privacy of no rear neighbors and a picturesque view of greenery. Conveniently situated near shopping centers, stores, restaurants, and schools, this home also offers easy access to Orlando and its thrilling theme parks, making it the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your dream home! Schedule a viewing today.
